        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "\"Friend Goat,\" said the tiger, \"here you have the opportunity to procure a beautiful necklace for your daughter, free of cost.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
