        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "The tiger looked up at him with an innocent expression and asked, \"Do you see any blood on me?\" There was no blood on the tiger, but the host looked into the next hammock and saw the goat all covered with blood.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
