        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "\"I know now who killed my fattest lamb,\" he said, and he gave the goat such a beating that the poor goat barely escaped with his life.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
