        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "The tiger went through the marsh and fell into the mud so that he was barely able to get out again.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "The monkey went around the marsh and walked on dry ground.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "After a while the tiger and the monkey came to the banana trees. \"Friend Monkey,\" said the tiger, \"aren't you hungry?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "Let us stop here and eat some bananas.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "You climb up and pluck the bananas.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "Give the ripe ones to me and you may keep the green ones for yourself.\" The monkey climbed up and picked the bananas but he ate all the ripe ones himself and threw the green ones down to the tiger.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000012_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000012_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "The tiger was forced to go hungry but the monkey had a good meal.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "Finally the tiger and the monkey came to a cobra lying in the path. \"Friend Monkey,\" said the tiger, \"here you have the opportunity to procure a beautiful necklace for your daughter, free of cost.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "Pick it up and it is yours.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "\"Pick it up yourself,\" replied the monkey.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "When the tiger and the monkey arrived at the house of the tiger's friend it was very late.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "They went to bed in hammocks hung up close together.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "The monkey had seen enough of the tiger that day to make him decide that he had better sleep with one eye open.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "Accordingly he pretended he was asleep, but he was really awake.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000015_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000015_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "At midnight he saw the tiger crawl quietly out of his hammock, walk on tip toe to the door, open it gently, and go out.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000015_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000015_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "The monkey decided to watch and see what happened when the tiger came back.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "The tiger went to the place where the sheep were kept, killed the fattest lamb of the flock and had a feast.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "When he came back he tried to wipe the lamb's blood on the monkey.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000016_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000016_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "The monkey saw him and gave him a push so that he spilled the blood all over himself and his own hammock.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "Early the next morning when the host missed one of his lambs he came to the room where his guests were sleeping.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5269_26555_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5269/26555/5269_26555_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5269",
        "content": "He saw the tiger all covered with blood and he cried, \"O ho, I have at last caught the one who kills my lambs.\" Then he gave the tiger such a beating that he barely escaped with his life.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    }
]